            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2019%3A1-21%3A17%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Message%20about%20Egypt%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20message%20came%20to%20me%20concerning%20Egypt%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3ELook!%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20advancing%20against%20Egypt%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eriding%20on%20a%20swift%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20idols%20of%20Egypt%20tremble.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20hearts%20of%20the%20Egyptians%20melt%20with%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20make%20Egyptian%20fight%20against%20Egyptian%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebrother%20against%20brother%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eneighbor%20against%20neighbor%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecity%20against%20city%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eprovince%20against%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Egyptians%20will%20lose%20heart%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20I%20will%20confuse%20their%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20will%20plead%20with%20their%20idols%20for%20wisdom%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20call%20on%20spirits%2C%20mediums%2C%20and%20those%20who%20consult%20the%20spirits%20of%20the%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20hand%20Egypt%20over%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20a%20hard%2C%20cruel%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EA%20fierce%20king%20will%20rule%20them%2C%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Esays%20the%20Lord%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20waters%20of%20the%20Nile%20will%20fail%20to%20rise%20and%20flood%20the%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20riverbed%20will%20be%20parched%20and%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20canals%20of%20the%20Nile%20will%20dry%20up%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20streams%20of%20Egypt%20will%20stink%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewith%20rotting%20reeds%20and%20rushes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20the%20greenery%20along%20the%20riverbank%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20all%20the%20crops%20along%20the%20river%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewill%20dry%20up%20and%20blow%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20fishermen%20will%20lament%20for%20lack%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThose%20who%20cast%20hooks%20into%20the%20Nile%20will%20groan%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20those%20who%20use%20nets%20will%20lose%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20flax%20for%20the%20harvesters%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eno%20thread%20for%20the%20weavers.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20will%20be%20in%20despair%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20all%20the%20workers%20will%20be%20sick%20at%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_11%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20fools%20are%20the%20officials%20of%20Zoan!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ETheir%20best%20counsel%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Egypt%20is%20stupid%20and%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWill%20they%20still%20boast%20to%20Pharaoh%20of%20their%20wisdom%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWill%20they%20dare%20brag%20about%20all%20their%20wise%20ancestors%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_12%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EWhere%20are%20your%20wise%20counselors%2C%20Pharaoh%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELet%20them%20tell%20you%20what%20God%20plans%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhat%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20is%20going%20to%20do%20to%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_13%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20officials%20of%20Zoan%20are%20fools%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20officials%20of%20Memphis%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E19%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ENoph.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20are%20deluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20people%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehave%20led%20Egypt%20astray.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_14%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20sent%20a%20spirit%20of%20foolishness%20on%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20all%20their%20suggestions%20are%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20cause%20Egypt%20to%20stagger%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20a%20drunk%20in%20his%20vomit.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_15%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20Egypt%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAll%20are%20helpless%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ethe%20head%20and%20the%20tail%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20noble%20palm%20branch%20and%20the%20lowly%20reed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_16%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20day%20the%20Egyptians%20will%20be%20as%20weak%20as%20women.%20They%20will%20cower%20in%20fear%20beneath%20the%20upraised%20fist%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_17%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EJust%20to%20speak%20the%20name%20of%20Israel%20will%20terrorize%20them%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20has%20laid%20out%20his%20plans%20against%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_18%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20day%20five%20of%20Egypt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20cities%20will%20follow%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%20They%20will%20even%20begin%20to%20speak%20Hebrew%2C%20the%20language%20of%20Canaan.%20One%20of%20these%20cities%20will%20be%20Heliopolis%2C%20the%20City%20of%20the%20Sun.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E19%3A18%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ewill%20be%20the%20City%20of%20Destruction.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_19_19%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20day%20there%20will%20be%20an%20altar%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Egypt%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20monument%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20at%20its%2